title: 173: DJ’s Top 50, Jabrill Peppers interview
itunes:title: 173: DJ’s Top 50, Jabrill Peppers interview
description:
In this episode of Move the Sticks, Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks talk to Michigan playmaker Jabrill Peppers and compare Myles Garrett’s draft stock to other NFL players when they came out of college. DJ reveals his Top 50 prospects and talks to Arizona general manager Steve Keim about the state of the Cardinals. The guys also give their perfect pairings for the top two picks of every NFC North team and look for some mid-round steals at wide receiver.
